<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
<title>Power Series vs. Numerical ODE Solution</title>
<script src="https://cdn.plot.ly/plotly-2.30.0.min.js"></script>
<style>
  html, body {
    height: 100%;
    margin: 0;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    color: #333;
    background: #fafafa;
  }
  #main-container {
    height: 100%;
    display: flex;
    gap: 12px;
