</head>
<body>
  <h1>Eratosthenes's Measure of the Earth's Circumference</h1>
  <p>
    Adjust the post angle measured at Alexandria and toggle the zoom view to explore how
    Eratosthenes related the shadow angle to the central angle between Syene and Alexandria.
  </p>

  <div id="control-panel">
