  <h1>Applying Graphics Filters Using Convolution</h1>
  <p class="description">Pick a letter, choose a filter, and see how convolution kernels transform a pixelated glyph.</p>

  <div id="control-panel">
    <div class="row">
      <label class="title" for="slider-convolver">convolver</label>
      <button class="mini-btn btn-minus" data-target="slider-convolver" aria-label="decrease convolver">−</button>
      <input type="range" id="slider-convolver" min="1" max="5" step="1" value="2" />
