<title>Carbon Cycle — Interactive Steps</title>
<style>
  body {
    margin: 0;
    font-family: system-ui, -apple-system, Segoe UI, Roboto, Helvetica, Arial, sans-serif;
    background: #ffffff;
  }
  #container {
    min-height: 100vh;
